00:07:38,917 --> 00:07:40,169
Bukan itu.

106
00:07:40,252 --> 00:07:41,587
Maksudku kasus pembunuhan itu.

107
00:07:42,963 --> 00:07:44,173
Mari kita akhiri.

108
00:07:45,632 --> 00:07:49,970
