144
00:11:49,209 --> 00:11:50,460
Baik, Pak.

145
00:11:53,296 --> 00:11:54,506
Ya, ini aku.

146
00:11:54,714 --> 00:11:58,677
Kaki orang yang pergi bengkok ke dalam.

147
00:11:59,052 --> 00:12:00,971
<i>Ini artinya lututnya bengkok.</i>

148
00:12:01,179 --> 00:12:03,348
